description:
Rewrapped - Season 1, Episode 4




Who You Callin' a CupCake?

In the Recreate Challenge, the competitors do their best to craft a stellar imitation of the Hostess CupCake, the godfather of snack cakes. In the Innovate Challenge, a competitor goes for the win with a wildly imaginative CupCake Chicken Mole. It's seven squiggles of snack-tacular fun in this chocolaty episode of Rewrapped!




Original Air Date: 05-May-2014
